This is a picture of me typing out a list. Five reasons you know you're getting old at festivals.
1) You know less than half the artists performing.
2) Seeing children with earmuffs on makes you jealous.
3) Water is your preferred drink.
4) The closer to the stage, the higher the anxiety.
5) You bring a fanny pack with ALL the essentials and constantly put on Sunscreen.
What's some of yours? 🤣😎
